### Top 5 Gaps (by priority)

1. **Scoring feedback loop is too thin** — Only 7% of predictions scored. The tool-weighting system can't learn. Increase scoring frequency to every 2h.

2. **72% of markets uncategorized** — 541 markets have no category, and "health" is entirely missing. Use Ollama to auto-classify market titles.

3. **GDELT & Reddit 25h stale** — Both non-market sources stopped updating. Market sources are fine. Need to investigate collector failures and add freshness alerts.

4. **Graph 84% disconnected** — 938 isolated nodes. Add embedding-similarity edges (cosine > 0.7) using existing MiniLM model to boost connectivity.

5. **29% of sources lack sentiment** — Run sentiment immediately after collection instead of on a separate schedule.

### Recommended Priority
**Scoring frequency > Auto-categorization > Graph connectivity > Freshness alerting**

The scoring loop is the single most impactful fix — without it, the system can't learn which prediction tools work best.
